ISLAMABAD, Sep 22 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb said on Thursday that Bill Gates called on Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif in New York.
In a tweet, she said the PM apprised him about human cost of climate change, food insecurity triggered by floods and plight of flood-stricken women and children.
